node.text:
🍭#KickSugar Giveaway 🍭

Win 24 bags of SmartSweets! 🎉

In the final episode of season one, the SmartSweets Squad gathers at Candyland HQ! The squad partakes in a fun activity called, “Can you imagine…?”, where each SmartSweets Squad Member express their dreams for SmartSweets! 🤩 ✨ Enter to win 24 bags of your fav #KickSugar flavour by telling us what you imagine or dream for SmartSweets to be in the years to come ✨🍭 Winner will be DMed tomorrow!

🎉VLOG GIVEAWAY🎉 
Do you want to know what flavour we are innovating next? This week @SmartSweetsFounder teases what #KickSugar candy you can expect this summer! Enter to win 24 bags of SmartSweets by commenting what flavour you want us to innovate next (only using emoji 🤪🍒)! 3 people will be randomly selected and DMed tomorrow. 🍭 Goodluck!

🎉 Win SmartSweets! 🎉⁣
⁣
In episode 2, @smartsweetsfounder is talking all things #StartUpLife and her approach to innovation since day one of recipe testing in her kitchen (including a preview of the Gummy Bear mold she bought off Amazon). ⁣
⁣
Can you recite the 7 stages of candy? 🍭 First 5 people to recite the 7 stages correctly win a 12 pack of their fav kick sugar candy!

node.text:
The secret is out 🤗 ... we are launching a vlog!! But real talk: can we rename it to something other than the word "vlog"? 🤔

This January, follow @SmartSweetsFounder (Tara Bosch) behind the scenes of innovating #KickSugar candy (and maybe find out what new juicy flavours you can expect in 2020 🙊). Excited? 🎉

We are obsessed with innovation and we can't wait to show you all that goes into making your #KickSugar dreams come true! 🍭

Tell us! What do you want to see on The Vlog? 💛

💛🍉 GIVEAWAY CLOSED 🍉💛 Congrats to our winner @shorty9889 🎉

GIVEAWAY! To celebrate #NationalWatermelonDay, we have partnered with @ElfCosmetics to giveaway a Jelly Poppin’ & #KickSugar watermelon prize pack! 🍉 Two lucky winners will receive a $100 elfcosmetics.com gift card and 24 bags of SmartSweets candy.

How to Enter:
🍉 Follow @elfcosmetics and @SmartSweets
🍉  Tag two (or more!) friends in the comments. Each tag counts as a separate entry.
🍉 BONUS: share this post to your IG Stories and tag us so we can see!

Giveaway starts now and ends Friday, August 6th 11:59 p.m. PT. NO PURCHASE NECESSARY. The winner will be chosen and contacted via direct message from verified accounts only. Open to USA and Canada residents over 18 (except Alaska and Hawaii)
